31:43.717 --> 31:46.184
Get the hell out of here.

31:59.765 --> 32:01.601
Goddamn robots.

32:51.851 --> 32:53.484
'"The Banana
Splits Adventure Hour"'

32:53.486 --> 32:55.553
'was first conceived in 1967'

32:55.555 --> 32:58.557
as a send-up of another popular
TV show from the era.

32:58.559 --> 32:59.624
Anyone know which one?

32:59.626 --> 33:02.226
Duh. "The Monkees."

33:02.228 --> 33:03.628
You know, "The Banana Splits"
was supposed

33:03.630 --> 33:05.463
to be called "Banana Bunch."

33:05.465 --> 33:08.934
But there was already
another movie by that name.

33:08.936 --> 33:10.801
Actually,
it was a children's book.

33:10.803 --> 33:12.803
Actually, I'm a pretty big fan

33:12.805 --> 33:13.938
so I think I'd know.

33:13.940 --> 33:16.374
Thadd, let it go.

33:16.376 --> 33:19.444
It's an incredibly sweet thing
you did for your brother.

33:19.446 --> 33:22.647
Hey, his dad sucks,
but I love him.

33:22.649 --> 33:25.849
