33:27.588 --> 33:30.421
Because he raised you like a son
for the last 11 years.

33:30.423 --> 33:33.891
Mom, mom, the guy's
a selfish prick. He hates me.

33:33.893 --> 33:35.793
He barely remembered
his own son's birthday.

33:35.795 --> 33:38.530
