He'd rather be at work.

33:38.532 --> 33:41.302
- It's not true.
- Then where is he?

33:49.275 --> 33:51.445
Just stay with your brother.
I'll be right back.

33:55.916 --> 33:57.881
Are you excited?

33:59.620 --> 34:00.985
'Everyone, stay clam.'

34:00.987 --> 34:04.688
I'm sure it's just...
"The Banana Splits."

34:04.690 --> 34:06.494
Oh, my God.

34:09.661 --> 34:11.728
If everybody can get in a line,
I'll make sure

34:11.731 --> 34:14.367
you all get photos
with the Splits.

34:27.280 --> 34:29.580
- Excuse me, miss?
- Uh, one moment, sir.

34:29.581 --> 34:32.382
Jonathan, please.
Call me Jonathan.

34:32.385 --> 34:34.385
Jonathan, you're next.
Just wait your turn.

34:36.755 --> 34:40.791
Uh, miss, excuse me. Miss?

34:40.793 --> 34:43.695
Go to our website
to download the photos.

34:43.697 --> 34:45.362
Dude, what?

34:45.364 --> 34:47.601
