to see the producer.

34:49.402 --> 34:51.503
What's on your cheek?

34:51.505 --> 34:53.536
Oh, I'm not sure.

34:53.539 --> 34:55.639
Must have rubbed off
of Drooper.

34:55.641 --> 34:58.579
I bet it's strawberry from
one of the Sloppy Time pies.

35:01.081 --> 35:03.316
Nope, that's not strawberry.

35:04.718 --> 35:06.450
I don't know what that is.

35:06.452 --> 35:10.354
I really think if the producer
saw Parker, he would...

35:10.356 --> 35:12.890
- She.
- She.

35:12.892 --> 35:14.925
She would realize
that she had a star

35:14.927 --> 35:16.628
standing right in front of her.

35:16.630 --> 35:18.762
She'd probably even
give you a promotion

35:18.764 --> 35:20.698
for making the introduction.

35:20.700 --> 35:23.667
- I can't do that.
- But..

35:23.669 --> 35:26.437
It's not gonna happen.

35:26.439 --> 35:28.039
O-okay.

35:28.041 --> 35:29.776
I understand.

35:32.979 --> 35:35.579
Hey, guys, are you excited
to get your photos?

35:35.581 --> 35:37.414
- Yes.
- Come on, Parker.

35:37.416 --> 35:39.818
We'll have to find
the producer ourselves.

35:44.825 --> 35:47.395
Hey! You can't go back there.

35:52.365 --> 35:55.066
- This is perfect. Come on.
- What are you doing?

35:55.068 --> 35:56.834
Let's check out
the rest of this place.

35:56.836 --> 35:59.037
We can go live
from another set.

35:59.039 --> 36:00.070
I don't think we should.

36:00.072 --> 36:01.673
Babe, it will be a moment

36:01.675 --> 36:04.041
we'll remember forever.

36:04.043 --> 36:06.413
- I promise.
- Okay.

36:08.548 --> 36:10.481
What about our pictures?

36:10.483 --> 36:12.517
Um, I'm sure she'll be back.

36:12.519 --> 36:13.785
Besides,
this is kind of awesome.

36:13.787 --> 36:15.790
You have the Splits
all to yourself.

36:18.023 --> 36:19.726
