37:41.974 --> 37:43.143
'Beth, don't.'

37:45.778 --> 37:48.680
- Oh, my God.
- I can explain.

37:48.682 --> 37:51.548
Like, how can you explain this?

37:51.550 --> 37:53.920
Are you sleeping with her?

38:00.526 --> 38:02.526
I can't believe this.

38:02.528 --> 38:04.195
I swear it was just one time.

38:04.197 --> 38:06.129
