38:32.057 --> 38:33.624
- Your dad's lucky he didn't...
- Don't talk about my dad.

38:33.626 --> 38:35.894
Okay, stop, stop it!
Go back inside, okay?

38:35.896 --> 38:37.896
- What're you gonna do about it?
- This is between us.

38:37.898 --> 38:39.963
Us?

38:39.965 --> 38:43.200
Beth, there's never been an us.

38:43.202 --> 38:45.840
There was always Austin
and then there was Harley.

38:47.807 --> 38:48.805
Us.

38:50.677 --> 38:52.111
What a joke.

38:53.847 --> 38:56.747
You know what?
You go inside and get the kids.

38:56.749 --> 38:59.085
I'll be at the car, okay?

39:00.887 --> 39:02.055
Us.

39:12.097 --> 39:14.899
- Mom, mom, stop. Stop.
- No, he is a dick.

39:14.901 --> 39:16.971
Yeah, yeah, I know, okay?

39:18.905 --> 39:21.939
Just wanted to be
with somebody safe

39:21.941 --> 39:24.611
