actually enjoying it.

40:20.200 --> 40:22.834
I dare you to open that.

40:22.836 --> 40:24.836
Why? What's gonna happen?

40:24.838 --> 40:26.303
'Open it. You'll see.'

40:26.305 --> 40:29.207
