40:29.209 --> 40:30.675
Ha.

40:35.215 --> 40:37.818
- Come on.
- Don't rush me.

40:46.992 --> 40:48.992
Was something
supposed to happen?

40:48.994 --> 40:52.195
When Drooper does it,
letters shoot out.

40:52.197 --> 40:55.301
Well, uh, there's nothing here.

40:57.202 --> 40:59.206
