42:41.474 --> 42:42.974
Just get the meet-and-greets
out of here

42:42.976 --> 42:44.977
and we'll start wrapping out
on Monday.

42:53.385 --> 42:56.120
I can't believe it.

42:56.122 --> 42:57.988
Thadd, this is amazing.

42:57.990 --> 43:00.927
That's Snorky's circus
and Bingo's jungle.

43:03.095 --> 43:05.296
Holy crap.

43:05.298 --> 43:08.198
That's Fleegle's Magic Shop.

43:08.200 --> 43:09.836
Oh, my gosh.

43:11.070 --> 43:13.303
FYI, the design
is loosely modeled

43:13.305 --> 43:16.006
of Davenport's Magic Shop
in London.

43:16.008 --> 43:19.079
This is like my whole childhood
right here.

43:21.014 --> 43:23.013
Babe, give me your phone.

43:30.356 --> 43:33.323
What's up, you guys?
It's your boy Thadd.

43:33.325 --> 43:36.394
Mr. Thadastic to all my fans.

43:36.396 --> 43:41.465
I'm here with the one
and only Miss Poppy Glarady

43:41.467 --> 43:45.001
and we're live on set
of "The Banana Splits."

43:45.003 --> 43:46.570
What up, everyone?

43:46.572 --> 43:49.106
We're alone
in Fleegle's Magic Shop.

43:49.108 --> 43:51.441
I can't even.

43:51.443 --> 43:54.313
Yo, check this out.
You're gonna love this.

44:02.488 --> 44:03.557
Hey, Pop?

44:05.925 --> 44:07.524
Thadd, no.

44:07.526 --> 44:09.861
Babe, I love you so much.

44:09.863 --> 44:12.229
'And I can't think
of a better place than this.'

44:12.231 --> 44:14.198
'Will you marry me?'

44:14.200 --> 44:15.466
Thadd, yes.

44:15.468 --> 44:17.968
Yo, she said yes!

44:17.970 --> 44:19.106
Oh.

44:33.919 --> 44:36.120
What the hell?

44:36.122 --> 44:37.558
Fleegle.

44:40.260 --> 44:42.062
We just got engaged.

44:43.528 --> 44:45.264
Hey.

44:51.169 --> 44:53.905
'Banana-cadabra!'

44:53.907 --> 44:56.274
- What the hell, man?
- Thadd, relax.

44:56.276 --> 44:58.212
I think he's just doing
a magic trick.

45:02.981 --> 45:04.550
What are you doing?

45:07.986 --> 45:09.287
Hey.

45:13.358 --> 45:15.992
- Poppy, please!
- Thadd.

45:15.994 --> 45:17.430
- Thadd!
- Let me out!

45:21.934 --> 45:23.934
Please let him out, please.

45:23.936 --> 45:25.468
No, please!

45:25.470 --> 45:28.638
No! Let him out. Please!

45:28.640 --> 45:30.474
Thadd. Thadd!

45:30.476 --> 45:32.008
- What's going on?
- 'No, please.'

45:32.010 --> 45:33.477
- Let me out.
- 'Thadd, please!'

45:33.479 --> 45:35.646
Let me out!

45:35.648 --> 45:37.615
No!

45:37.617 --> 45:40.017
'No!'

45:40.019 --> 45:41.551
- Poppy.
- 'No!'

45:41.553 --> 45:43.222
- Stop!
- Please.

45:45.224 --> 45:47.361
- Thadd!
- Aah!

45:49.963 --> 45:51.629
Thadd.

45:51.631 --> 45:53.330
'No!'

45:53.332 --> 45:55.198
'No, please.'

45:55.200 --> 45:58.234
No!

46:03.209 --> 46:05.412
Please don't make me. Please!

46:08.548 --> 46:10.284
No!

46:37.343 --> 46:39.376
Ta-da!

46:42.548 --> 46:45.282
No. No, please. No!

46:45.284 --> 46:47.954
Get off of me! Get off!

46:53.191 --> 46:56.126
Please, no!

46:56.128 --> 46:58.064
- No.
- 'Snorky?'

47:00.767 --> 47:03.370
'Here's the circus.
He's got to be here.'

47:16.715 --> 47:18.351
Fleegle!

47:22.789 --> 47:24.758
Do you know where Snorky is?

47:27.727 --> 47:29.593
Can you take us to him?

47:29.595 --> 47:31.698
Harley really
wants to meet Snorky.

47:45.811 --> 47:48.681
Come on. You wanna meet Snorky.
Don't ya?

48:18.244 --> 48:20.514
Oh, Kara, you are killing me.

49:24.543 --> 49:27.577
Daddy, I just wanna go home.

49:27.579 --> 49:30.713
Not until I get you
a real audition.

49:30.715 --> 49:34.318
We've worked too hard
to give up now. Hm?

49:34.320 --> 49:35.722
Come on.

49:46.932 --> 49:49.535
Are you ready to meet
your next superstar?

49:52.505 --> 49:54.872
Hey!

49:54.874 --> 49:56.974
I'm talking to you.

50:02.847 --> 50:04.847
Daddy, I'm scared.

50:04.849 --> 50:07.286
You don't have to be scared,
honey. It's just a puppet.

50:49.695 --> 50:51.762
Where is everybody?

50:51.764 --> 50:54.698
- They were all here.
- They're not with you?

50:54.700 --> 50:57.367
They're probably just exploring
the rest of the sets.

50:57.369 --> 50:59.470
- Harley! Zoe!
- Shit.

50:59.472 --> 51:02.573
Mom, uh, we'll find them.
It's fine.

51:02.575 --> 51:05.642
- You don't know that. Harley!
- Shit.

51:05.644 --> 51:07.644
- 'Zoe!'
- I promise, they're okay.

51:07.646 --> 51:09.379
Yeah, yeah, I know.

51:09.381 --> 51:11.383
My mom just..
She sometimes gets this way.

51:12.550 --> 51:15.285
We'll find them. Trust me.

51:15.287 --> 51:17.553
Can't even get off the lot
at this time of night.

51:17.555 --> 51:19.390
Somebody help me!

51:22.294 --> 51:24.563
Why are you doing this to me?

51:46.017 --> 51:49.722
Help! There's this psycho
tryin' to run me over!

51:52.090 --> 51:55.591
Oh, thank God.

51:55.593 --> 51:58.595
Hey.

51:58.597 --> 52:00.798
Did you hear me?

52:07.506 --> 52:08.705
'Mom,
Paige went to look for them.'

52:08.707 --> 52:10.774
She knows this place
better than anybody.

52:10.776 --> 52:13.343
I can't believe Harley
would just run off like that.

52:13.345 --> 52:14.711
You know him.
He's in his own world.

52:14.713 --> 52:16.446
He was probably just excited.

52:16.448 --> 52:17.983
If something happens to him, I..

52:19.852 --> 52:22.986
This is.. I don't, I don't know
if I can go through that again.

52:22.988 --> 52:24.887
We are at a taping
of "The Banana Splits."

52:24.889 --> 52:26.492
Nobody's gonna die.

52:29.662 --> 52:32.495
You weren't like this
when dad was alive.

52:32.497 --> 52:33.664
You were fearless.

52:33.666 --> 52:34.865
I watched him die

52:34.867 --> 52:36.367
and I couldn't stop it.

52:36.369 --> 52:38.102
It wasn't your fault.

52:38.104 --> 52:40.504
Bad things happen, you still..

52:40.506 --> 52:42.575
You know, we still need to live.

52:44.376 --> 52:48.379
I know that you think
I worry too much.

52:48.381 --> 52:50.414
'And that our life is boring,
but I..'

52:50.416 --> 52:52.852
I am just trying
to keep you guys all safe.

52:57.590 --> 52:58.955
Did you find them?

52:58.957 --> 53:00.858
Paige brought me up to speed
on the whole situation

53:00.860 --> 53:02.925
and I assure you
everything is under control.

53:08.700 --> 53:11.568
- Oh!
- Oh, my God!

53:11.570 --> 53:14.604
God, it's that stage dad.

53:14.606 --> 53:16.840
Sir, can-can you hear me?
What happened?

53:16.842 --> 53:20.910
They attacked me.

53:20.912 --> 53:23.717
- Who did?
- Banana Splits.

53:24.983 --> 53:26.452
Paige, call 911.

53:27.952 --> 53:29.753
Go!

53:29.755 --> 53:31.053
There has to be an explanation.

53:31.055 --> 53:33.689
Th-the Banana Splits
don't hurt people.

53:39.865 --> 53:42.533
We have to get the kids.

53:42.535 --> 53:45.936
Uh, okay, just take..
Keep-keep breathing.

53:49.707 --> 53:51.508
What is this place?

53:51.510 --> 53:53.847
This must be where they were
built or something.

53:55.447 --> 53:57.416
Is Snorky in here?

54:00.186 --> 54:01.821
In there?

54:04.590 --> 54:06.392
This is weird.

54:11.063 --> 54:12.796
Hello? Snorky?

54:12.798 --> 54:14.700
Get me out of here!

54:18.037 --> 54:20.169
I brought friends.

54:28.680 --> 54:31.117
We're gonna have so much fun!

54:39.858 --> 54:42.194
Harley! Zoe!

54:44.095 --> 54:46.696
Mom, this is crazy, right?

54:46.698 --> 54:48.899
He loves this show.
Maybe he's hiding somewhere.

54:48.901 --> 54:50.233
He-he probably
doesn't wanna leave.

54:50.235 --> 54:51.602
Harley!

54:51.604 --> 54:53.604
Where are you?

54:53.606 --> 54:55.972
Come on. Come on, hurry.

54:55.974 --> 54:58.175
Harley! Zoe!

54:58.177 --> 54:59.609
Harley!

55:01.847 --> 55:03.917
- What's that noise?
- Bingo.

55:05.885 --> 55:07.149
'Mom!'

55:08.820 --> 55:10.122
Austin!

55:12.224 --> 55:14.561
Austin!

55:17.997 --> 55:19.896
Mom!

55:19.898 --> 55:21.867
Get out of here.

55:23.102 --> 55:24.637
Run!

55:42.320 --> 55:44.988
Time's almost up.

55:44.990 --> 55:46.256
For you.

56:04.642 --> 56:06.713
Mom,
that was seriously badass.

56:08.881 --> 56:10.817
Let's go find your brother.

56:24.729 --> 56:26.729
Oh, my God.

56:29.735 --> 56:31.704
He asked me to marry him.

56:33.805 --> 56:35.909
Mom, I think she's lost it.

56:38.876 --> 56:40.612
I'm so sorry.

56:44.082 --> 56:46.350
I'm looking for my son
and his friend.

56:46.352 --> 56:48.318
Have you seen them?

56:48.320 --> 56:50.720
- Fleegle took them.
- What?

56:50.722 --> 56:52.659
Where-where,
where did there go?

56:56.195 --> 56:58.260
Listen to me. Listen,
it's not safe here for you.

56:58.262 --> 57:00.631
You have to come with us, okay?

57:00.633 --> 57:02.265
I won't leave Thadd.

57:02.267 --> 57:05.001
I know how you feel. Trust me.

57:05.003 --> 57:07.206
He would not want anything bad
to happen to you.

57:08.807 --> 57:10.776
You have to come with us
right now.

57:41.740 --> 57:44.243
Hey, you gotta let us
out of here.

57:48.414 --> 57:50.713
- I can't.
- Of course, you can.

57:50.715 --> 57:52.749
Just unlock the gate.

57:52.751 --> 57:54.785
I tried to tell them
that it's wrong

57:54.787 --> 57:57.220
but they wouldn't listen.

57:57.222 --> 57:59.122
'Something went wrong
with my update.'

57:59.124 --> 58:01.425
They didn't listen to me now.

58:01.427 --> 58:04.227
This is all the network's fault.

58:04.229 --> 58:07.229
They shouldn't have taken away
their show.

58:07.231 --> 58:10.302
'Then none of
this would have happened.'

58:11.769 --> 58:15.271
This show is all they have.

58:20.345 --> 58:22.479
You built them, didn't you?

58:22.481 --> 58:25.251
- Yes.
- You love them, don't you?

58:27.218 --> 58:29.452
- Yes.
- I love them too.

58:29.454 --> 58:32.891
They're my favorite.
They make people happy.

58:34.325 --> 58:35.959
That's why I built them.

58:35.961 --> 58:38.195
But now they're hurting people.

58:38.197 --> 58:41.367
You can stop this, but you
have to let us out of here.

59:03.889 --> 59:06.055
Come on!

59:17.769 --> 59:19.104
Fleegle!

59:23.307 --> 59:26.178
My precious boy.
Who-who did this to you?

59:40.425 --> 59:43.492
Hi, kids.
Put on your hap-happiest faces

59:43.494 --> 59:46.331
because "The Banana Splits" show
is about to begin.

01:00:07.285 --> 01:00:09.789
'I can fix you. Wait.'

01:00:12.890 --> 01:00:14.124
Where do you think
you're going?

01:00:24.970 --> 01:00:26.872
Help! Ah!

01:00:29.474 --> 01:00:31.110
You'll never stop them!

01:00:33.044 --> 01:00:35.345
The show must go on!

01:00:35.347 --> 01:00:37.012
Everything's going to be okay.

01:00:37.014 --> 01:00:39.548
The, the ambulance
will be here soon.

01:00:39.550 --> 01:00:41.584
Where the hell are they?

01:00:46.157 --> 01:00:48.326
It's Sloppy Time!

01:00:49.494 --> 01:00:50.997
Oh, no.

01:00:54.365 --> 01:00:55.802
Stand down.

01:00:58.135 --> 01:01:00.236
I'm ordering you to stand down.

01:01:24.296 --> 01:01:25.495
No.

01:01:39.577 --> 01:01:41.111
Damn it.

01:02:31.229 --> 01:02:32.995
What's happening?

01:02:32.997 --> 01:02:35.198
We..

01:02:35.200 --> 01:02:37.470
We have to run
the Sloppy Time course.

01:02:55.519 --> 01:02:57.454
- Oh, come on.
- Give me, give me your hand.

01:03:39.231 --> 01:03:42.068
Don't stop now.
You're almost there.

01:03:49.140 --> 01:03:51.077
We're gonna make it.

01:04:00.651 --> 01:04:02.420
Where's the blue key?

01:04:15.434 --> 01:04:17.503
It's time to fly!

01:04:24.508 --> 01:04:27.843
I, I did it.

01:04:27.845 --> 01:04:30.015
I did it.

01:04:31.682 --> 01:04:33.316
Don't hit the hammer.

01:04:36.387 --> 01:04:38.454
She did it!

01:04:38.456 --> 01:04:41.256
He took it down
to Hammer Town.

01:04:42.561 --> 01:04:44.861
Three cheers for Rebecca!

01:04:44.863 --> 01:04:47.162
'Hip hip hooray!'

01:05:03.682 --> 01:05:05.618
Which way do we go?

01:05:15.660 --> 01:05:17.329
It's locked.

01:05:22.434 --> 01:05:24.637
I'll take him out.
You guys run.

01:05:33.144 --> 01:05:36.114
What are you doing?
We can't trust him.

01:05:37.349 --> 01:05:39.584
It's Snorky. He's different.

01:05:49.894 --> 01:05:55.265
♪ Tra la la la-la la la ♪

01:05:55.267 --> 01:05:59.305
♪ Tra la la la-la la la ♪

01:06:03.675 --> 01:06:08.711
♪ Tra la la la-la la la ♪

01:06:08.713 --> 01:06:12.715
♪ Tra la la la-la la la ♪♪

01:06:12.717 --> 01:06:15.517
Are they doing
the Snorky Shuffle?

01:06:15.519 --> 01:06:17.456
This is some messed up stuff
right here.

01:06:18.822 --> 01:06:20.492
Please, Snorky.

01:06:22.793 --> 01:06:24.561
Help us.

01:06:39.311 --> 01:06:40.778
It's okay, guys.

01:07:18.883 --> 01:07:22.919
♪ Tra la la la-la la la ♪

01:07:22.921 --> 01:07:26.823
♪ Tra la la la-la la la ♪

01:07:26.825 --> 01:07:30.727
♪ Tra la la la-la la la ♪

01:07:30.729 --> 01:07:34.896
♪ Tra la la la-la la la ♪

01:07:34.898 --> 01:07:38.767
♪ Tra la la la-la la la ♪

01:07:38.769 --> 01:07:42.974
♪ Tra la la la-la la la ♪♪

01:08:15.606 --> 01:08:17.372
Hey. Hey.

01:08:17.375 --> 01:08:19.609
Hey, shh, don't worry.

01:08:19.611 --> 01:08:21.644
You scared the hell out of me.

01:08:21.645 --> 01:08:23.613
Are the police coming?

01:08:23.615 --> 01:08:24.779
No, the phones don't work

01:08:24.782 --> 01:08:26.515
and all the cell phones
were smashed.

01:08:26.518 --> 01:08:29.319
We have to find Fleegle.
They took Harley and Zoe.

01:08:29.321 --> 01:08:31.354
We have to stop them.

01:08:31.356 --> 01:08:33.788
There must be a way
to stop them.

01:08:33.791 --> 01:08:34.926
Karl.

01:08:36.661 --> 01:08:37.930
Come on.

01:08:50.375 --> 01:08:51.908
Yo! Shit.

01:08:53.678 --> 01:08:56.048
- Austin. Austin! Austin!
- Don't you touch him!

01:08:57.549 --> 01:08:58.984
Karl?

01:09:02.554 --> 01:09:03.984
How do we stop
the Banana Splits?

01:09:06.724 --> 01:09:08.390
You can't.

01:09:08.393 --> 01:09:09.890
You built them.
There must be a way.

01:09:09.893 --> 01:09:12.560
The show must go on.

01:09:12.563 --> 01:09:13.995
It's in their programming.

01:09:16.500 --> 01:09:18.036
They took my kids.

01:09:19.837 --> 01:09:21.904
Your children are safe.

01:09:21.906 --> 01:09:26.140
Mm, they're having
a wonderful time.

01:09:31.982 --> 01:09:33.551
Is that music?

01:09:37.755 --> 01:09:39.791
Sounds like it's coming
from down there.

01:09:42.826 --> 01:09:44.529
Help me move this.

01:09:50.468 --> 01:09:53.468
- What's down there?
- The show.

01:10:05.650 --> 01:10:06.919
Let's go.

01:10:17.929 --> 01:10:19.194
What is that?

01:10:19.196 --> 01:10:22.667
I was building a sister
for my boys.

01:10:23.634 --> 01:10:26.468
A fifth Banana Split?

01:10:26.470 --> 01:10:28.674
Her name is Hooty.

01:10:31.476 --> 01:10:33.445
We were gonna get married.

01:10:38.650 --> 01:10:40.619
But then they killed him.

01:10:52.129 --> 01:10:54.400
What are you doing?

01:10:56.567 --> 01:10:59.537
Stop that! It's not for you.

01:11:09.613 --> 01:11:12.013
'Stay back!'

01:11:15.586 --> 01:11:17.589
He's dead because of you.

01:11:31.936 --> 01:11:34.569
'Where's Poppy?
She was right behind me.'

01:11:34.571 --> 01:11:36.641
'She'll catch up. Come on.'

01:12:33.063 --> 01:12:35.730
What, uh, what is that
in his eyes?

01:12:35.732 --> 01:12:37.900
Bing-Bingo's drumsticks.

01:12:37.902 --> 01:12:39.601
It's Doug. The other page.

01:12:39.603 --> 01:12:41.807
They sent him out
with the rest of the audience.

01:12:47.778 --> 01:12:50.648
- Oh, Jesus.
- It's only the adults.

01:12:54.686 --> 01:12:57.052
Where are the children?

01:13:00.791 --> 01:13:02.059
Let's go.

01:13:28.251 --> 01:13:31.119
Ta-da!

01:13:34.692 --> 01:13:36.962
Well, who could that be?

01:13:49.874 --> 01:13:52.644
Look who I found.
It's Stevie.

01:13:53.777 --> 01:13:54.810
What the hell is this?

01:13:54.812 --> 01:13:56.712
Isn't it wonderful, Stevie?

01:13:56.714 --> 01:13:58.814
All of our friends are here.

01:13:58.816 --> 01:14:00.382
Now the show can go on

01:14:00.384 --> 01:14:04.188
'forever and ever and ever!'

01:14:05.689 --> 01:14:07.789
They're never gonna let them go.

01:14:07.791 --> 01:14:10.092
They'll die in here.

01:14:10.094 --> 01:14:11.761
We have to save those kids.

01:14:25.876 --> 01:14:29.214
Hey, Stevie. Mail's here!

01:14:43.061 --> 01:14:44.793
Shh.

01:14:55.238 --> 01:14:56.971
Silly Stevie.

01:14:56.973 --> 01:15:00.943
Smoking's bad for your health.

01:15:00.945 --> 01:15:04.148
- I can't see Harley or Zoe.
- Maybe they got away.

01:15:09.920 --> 01:15:12.721
Oh, boy, it's time for..

01:15:12.723 --> 01:15:15.427
- The wheel of endings.
- The wheel of endings.

01:15:33.277 --> 01:15:35.714
I'm the vice president
of Programming.

01:15:36.880 --> 01:15:39.448
You can't do this to me.

01:15:39.450 --> 01:15:41.449
We have to hurry.

01:15:46.256 --> 01:15:48.923
I wonder
how the show is gonna end.

01:15:54.965 --> 01:15:56.168
Guys.

01:15:58.068 --> 01:15:59.470
Take it slow.

01:16:11.281 --> 01:16:13.516
Oh, my God.

01:16:13.518 --> 01:16:16.185
Great job, Snorky.

01:16:16.187 --> 01:16:18.457
Put them
with our other friends.

01:16:25.897 --> 01:16:28.830
You can't do this.
You're the Banana Splits.

01:16:28.832 --> 01:16:31.103
The show must go on.

01:16:37.942 --> 01:16:40.212
Snorky, please don't do this.

01:17:07.437 --> 01:17:10.940
Banana split!

01:17:10.942 --> 01:17:13.278
What, what's a banana split?

01:17:14.978 --> 01:17:17.312
What's a banana split?

01:17:17.314 --> 01:17:18.980
- What's a banana split?
- I don't know.

01:17:18.982 --> 01:17:21.283
It always lands on rock out.

01:17:26.122 --> 01:17:27.422
Mom.

01:17:27.424 --> 01:17:28.891
Everybody, close your eyes.

01:17:28.893 --> 01:17:30.292
'Close your eyes!
Don't watch this.'

01:18:13.437 --> 01:18:14.906
Come on, guys.

01:18:18.142 --> 01:18:20.008
Austin, Paige,
take the kids out.

01:18:20.010 --> 01:18:21.243
Go.

01:18:24.180 --> 01:18:25.280
I'm not gonna leave you behind.

01:18:25.282 --> 01:18:27.917
Grab Harley and Zoey and go.

01:18:27.919 --> 01:18:29.618
Go!

